SELECT , , , , CASE WHEN jigyoutaishousha_jyukyusha."kubun" IS NULL THEN '3' ELSE jigyoutaishousha_jyukyusha."kubun" END AS "kubun" , , CASE WHEN "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."koikinaiJushochiTokureiFlag" = '1' THEN "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."koikinaiTokureiSochimotoShichosonCode" ELSE "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."shichosonCode" END AS "shokisaiHihokenshaNo",
FROM ( SELECT * FROM rgdb."DbV3113RiyoshaFutanWariai" WHERE "nendo"=#{年度} AND "hakoFuyoFlag"= false
AND "insertTimestamp" >= #{抽出期間開始日時} AND "insertTimestamp" < #{抽出期間終了日時}
AND "hakoYMD" is null
AND "hakoYMD" is not null
AND "hihokenshaNo" IN ( SELECT DISTINCT "hihokenshaNo" FROM rgdb."DbT4001JukyushaDaicho" WHERE "insertTimestamp" >= #{抽出期間開始日時} AND "insertTimestamp" < #{抽出期間終了日時} AND "yukoMukoKubun" = '1' AND "logicalDeletedFlag" = false AND "chokkinIdoJiyuCode" IN ('01', '02', '04', '10') UNION SELECT DISTINCT "hihokenshaNo" FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" WHERE "insertTimestamp" >= #{抽出期間開始日時} AND "insertTimestamp" < #{抽出期間終了日時} )
) AS "DbT3113RiyoshaFutanWariai" LEFT OUTER JOIN rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" as "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho" ON "DbT3113RiyoshaFutanWariai"."hihokenshaNo" = "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."hihokenshaNo" LEFT OUTER JOIN AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."shikibetsuCode" = "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode" LEFT OUTER JOIN AS "Atesaki" ON "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."shikibetsuCode" = "Atesaki"."shikibetsuCode" LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT "hihokenshaNo" , '2' AS "kubun" FROM rgdb."DbT4001JukyushaDaicho" WHERE "ninteiYukoKikanKaishiYMD" <= #{交付年月日} AND "ninteiYukoKikanShuryoYMD" >= #{交付年月日} AND "yukoMukoKubun" = '1' AND "logicalDeletedFlag" = false UNION SELECT DISTINCT "hiHokenshaNo" , '1' AS "kubun" FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" WHERE "ninteiYukoKaishiYMD" <= #{交付年月日} AND "ninteiYukoShuryoYMD" >= #{交付年月日} ) AS jigyoutaishousha_jyukyusha ON "DbT3113RiyoshaFutanWariai"."hihokenshaNo" = jigyoutaishousha_jyukyusha."hihokenshaNo" LEFT OUTER JOIN "FutanWariKikanTemp" AS FutanWariKikanTemp ON "DbT3113RiyoshaFutanWariai"."hihokenshaNo" = FutanWariKikanTemp."hihokenshaNo" LEFT OUTER JOIN rgdb."DbT7037ShoKofuKaishu" AS "DbT7037ShoKofuKaishu" ON "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."hihokenshaNo" = "DbT7037ShoKofuKaishu"."hihokenshaNo"
